      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "They're installing cameras next month. The engagement scoring starts in the fall. We were told it 'helps teachers identify disengaged students' but we've heard it also generates reports that go to the principal."
      },
      {
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "So the cameras go in next month, and the scoring follows later. That's actually useful — you have some time. The fact that you haven't been given details about where reports go or how scores are calculated is exactly the kind of thing your group can push on. You said thirty teachers met. Is your union involved, or is this informal so far?"
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "Informal so far, but our union president was at the meeting. She's supportive but wants to know what we're actually asking for before the union takes a position."
